    <title>St John the Evangelist&#039;s Feast in Constantim, Portugal</title>
    <link>http://www.demotix.com/news/552623/st-john-evangelists-feast-constantim-portugal</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-datetime field-field-date&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Monday, 27 December, 2010 - 09:45&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
